00:19:08.610 --> 00:19:13.390 align:middle line:84%
back over your life and you
can find times when something

00:19:13.390 --> 00:19:16.530 align:middle line:90%
happened that wasn't a result--

00:19:16.530 --> 00:19:17.330 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Scripted.

00:19:17.330 --> 00:19:18.830 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: That
wasn't scripted, that

