00:19:56.910 --> 00:19:57.720 align:middle line:90%
when it did happen.

00:19:57.720 --> 00:19:58.845 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, the feeling.

00:19:58.845 --> 00:20:02.650 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: And what is--
