Now, dreaming-- all
of these principles,

00:22:20.620 --> 00:22:22.090 align:middle line:90%
I had to give words to them.

00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:22.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:22:22.890 --> 00:22:24.348 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: But all
of the words mean

00:22:24.348 --> 00:22:25.970 align:middle line:84%
something slightly
different than they

00:22:25.970 --> 00:22:29.050 align:middle line:90%
do in our mundane vernacular.

00:22:29.050 --> 00:22:32.040 align:middle line:84%
So dreaming as a
spiritual practice

00:22:32.040 --> 00:22:40.050 align:middle line:84%
is about being able to hear
the information of the void,

00:22:40.050 --> 00:22:45.140 align:middle line:84%
being able to hear, go
into that great cosmic soup

00:22:45.140 --> 00:22:50.770 align:middle line:84%
of all potential and hear the
