00:22:50.770 --> 00:22:52.260 align:middle line:90%
brought into consciousness.

00:22:52.260 --> 00:22:54.510 align:middle line:90%
That's what dreaming is.

00:22:54.510 --> 00:22:57.380 align:middle line:84%
So you are, by
nature, a dreamer.

00:22:57.380 --> 00:23:02.050 align:middle line:84%
You are, by nature, the most--
the most deeply embedded piece

00:23:02.050 --> 00:23:06.160 align:middle line:84%
of your garment is that you
can hear information out

00:23:06.160 --> 00:23:06.960 align:middle line:90%
of the void.

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:08.709 align:middle line:84%
Now, sometimes, that
will come when you're

00:23:08.709 --> 00:23:10.390 align:middle line:90%
asleep in the form of a dream.

00:23:10.390 --> 00:23:12.770 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, it comes in
the form of daydreams.

00:23:12.770 --> 00:23:16.830 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes, it just pops
at you in those rare moments

00:23:16.830 --> 00:23:22.830 align:middle line:84%
when fear and should's and--
and willfulness have just

00:23:22.830 --> 00:23:24.490 align:middle line:90%
fallen away for a moment.

00:23:24.490 --> 00:23:25.290 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:23:25.290 --> 00:23:27.620 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: So-- so
that's what I would

00:23:27.620 --> 00:23:32.480 align:middle line:84%
