that you have come
to express, allowed

00:28:01.940 --> 00:28:04.030 align:middle line:90%
to be expressed through you.

00:28:04.030 --> 00:28:06.640 align:middle line:84%
And that's really kind of
what people are looking for.

00:28:06.640 --> 00:28:08.639 align:middle line:84%
How many people are
wandering around the planet,

00:28:08.639 --> 00:28:09.860 align:middle line:90%
what am I doing here?

00:28:09.860 --> 00:28:11.940 align:middle line:84%
What am I supposed
to do with my life?

00:28:11.940 --> 00:28:13.140 align:middle line:90%
What's this all about?

00:28:13.140 --> 00:28:15.160 align:middle line:84%
Well, that is really
the beauty, I think,

00:28:15.160 --> 00:28:18.230 align:middle line:90%
of what your work shows is that.

00:28:18.230 --> 00:28:20.430 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about
the work itself now.

00:28:20.430 --> 00:28:21.670 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: All right.

00:28:21.670 --> 00:28:22.470 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:28:22.470 --> 00:28:26.630 align:middle line:84%
So as I said, after this
experience with my father's

00:28:26.630 --> 00:28:31.610 align:middle line:84%
death, we did-- we went through
the business of his dying

00:28:31.610 --> 00:28:34.396 align:middle line:84%
and burying and
doing all of that.

00:28:34.396 --> 00:28:35.520 align:middle line:90%
And then, I went back home.

00:28:35.520 --> 00:28:37.500 align:middle line:84%
And as I said, I
started waking up

00:28:37.500 --> 00:28:40.750 align:middle line:84%
every night just about, around
3:00, 3:30 in the morning.

00:28:40.750 --> 00:28:42.000 align:middle line:90%
And I would write for a while.

00:28:42.000 --> 00:28:45.570 align:middle line:84%
And then, after a few months,
this body of information

00:28:45.570 --> 00:28:49.490 align:middle line:90%
had clarified itself.

00:28:49.490 --> 00:28:52.570 align:middle line:84%
There are 30
spiritual principles

00:28:52.570 --> 00:28:58.125 align:middle line:84%
that interweave to create the
human species, the human form.

00:28:58.125 --> 00:29:00.710 align:middle line:90%


00:29:00.710 --> 00:29:02.950 align:middle line:84%
Those 30 spiritual
principles each have

00:29:02.950 --> 00:29:07.360 align:middle line:84%
a numerological correspondence,
numbered 0 through 29.

00:29:07.360 --> 00:29:10.550 align:middle line:90%


00:29:10.550 --> 00:29:13.490 align:middle line:84%
Every sign in the
zodiac also has

00:29:13.490 --> 00:29:17.950 align:middle line:84%
a numerological correspondence,
numbered 0 through 29.

00:29:17.950 --> 00:29:20.100 align:middle line:84%
So that's how you
find your principles.

00:29:20.100 --> 00:29:22.860 align:middle line:84%
You look at your
natal chart, which is

00:29:22.860 --> 00:29:24.390 align:middle line:90%
what I've done here with yours.

00:29:24.390 --> 00:29:26.640 align:middle line:84%
This is, like, just a
typical round natal chart.

00:29:26.640 --> 00:29:27.440 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:29:27.440 --> 00:29:31.010 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: And you
look at the degrees

00:29:31.010 --> 00:29:33.100 align:middle line:90%
of your various planets.

00:29:33.100 --> 00:29:37.890 align:middle line:84%
So your son is at 22
degrees of Scorpio.

00:29:37.890 --> 00:29:42.420 align:middle line:84%
So on the chart, 22 corresponds
to the principle of dreaming.

00:29:42.420 --> 00:29:45.750 align:middle line:84%
So we know that dreaming is
your primary principle, and et

00:29:45.750 --> 00:29:46.550 align:middle line:90%
cetera, et cetera.

00:29:46.550 --> 00:29:51.010 align:middle line:84%
You go all the way through
the 12th, the sun and the moon

00:29:51.010 --> 00:29:52.980 align:middle line:84%
and the eight planets
and the Midheaven.

00:29:52.980 --> 00:29:56.220 align:middle line:84%
And you know, there are
certain configuration

00:29:56.220 --> 00:29:57.980 align:middle line:90%
of how you look at it.

00:29:57.980 --> 00:30:02.790 align:middle line:84%
And that's how you find out
what your principles are.

00:30:02.790 --> 00:30:06.720 align:middle line:84%
Then, the information
goes a little bit deeper.

00:30:06.720 --> 00:30:10.680 align:middle line:84%
The first 10 principles,
numbered 0 through 9,

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:13.570 align:middle line:84%
are directly
connected to nature.

00:30:13.570 --> 00:30:16.770 align:middle line:84%
They are like principles that
are coming up out of the earth,

00:30:16.770 --> 00:30:18.750 align:middle line:84%
out of nature, out of
the animal kingdom,

00:30:18.750 --> 00:30:21.710 align:middle line:84%
out of the stone
kingdom to be expressed

00:30:21.710 --> 00:30:25.150 align:middle line:90%
through the human psyche.

00:30:25.150 --> 00:30:27.930 align:middle line:84%
They're called the
ascending principles.

00:30:27.930 --> 00:30:30.750 align:middle line:84%
The top 10 principles,
number 20 through 29,

00:30:30.750 --> 00:30:33.640 align:middle line:84%
are-- we call-- what we call
the galactic principles.

00:30:33.640 --> 00:30:35.580 align:middle line:84%
They are principles
that can't even

00:30:35.580 --> 00:30:40.090 align:middle line:84%
really be described, like
love and peace and silence.

00:30:40.090 --> 00:30:43.520 align:middle line:84%
They're the very-- the highest
frequency of principles.

00:30:43.520 --> 00:30:46.320 align:middle line:84%
They are descending
to be expressed

00:30:46.320 --> 00:30:48.990 align:middle line:90%
through human, the human realm.

00:30:48.990 --> 00:30:50.710 align:middle line:84%
And then, the
middle 10 principles

00:30:50.710 --> 00:30:52.780 align:middle line:84%
are called the containing
principles, numbered 10

00:30:52.780 --> 00:30:53.870 align:middle line:90%
through 19.

00:30:53.870 --> 00:30:56.670 align:middle line:84%
And they are the principles that
are very, very human in nature,

00:30:56.670 --> 00:31:01.470 align:middle line:84%
like creativity and
intelligence and focus.

00:31:01.470 --> 00:31:05.180 align:middle line:84%
So if you were looking
at this as a tree,

00:31:05.180 --> 00:31:07.900 align:middle line:84%
the first 10 principles would
be the roots of the tree.

00:31:07.900 --> 00:31:11.390 align:middle line:84%
The middle 10 principles would
be the trunk of the tree.

00:31:11.390 --> 00:31:15.200 align:middle line:84%
And the top 10 principles
would be the leaves.

00:31:15.200 --> 00:31:16.090 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Foliage.

00:31:16.090 --> 00:31:18.420 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Yes, the light-eating
principles of the tree.

00:31:18.420 --> 00:31:19.320 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, yes.

00:31:19.320 --> 00:31:24.530 align:middle line:10%
>>KAPLAN: And they all function
together in a perfect way.

00:31:24.530 --> 00:31:29.180 align:middle line:10%
There is no conflict between
ascending and descending

00:31:29.180 --> 00:31:29.980 align:middle line:10%
principles.

00:31:29.980 --> 00:31:32.590 align:middle line:90%
They need each other, you know.

00:31:32.590 --> 00:31:36.895 align:middle line:84%
The leaves cannot eat the
light without the roots.

00:31:36.895 --> 00:31:37.770 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:31:37.770 --> 00:31:41.210 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: So that's what
the soul looks like.

00:31:41.210 --> 00:31:43.750 align:middle line:84%
That's what the human
soul looks like.

00:31:43.750 --> 00:31:45.530 align:middle line:84%
Can I go into talking
about the soul?

00:31:45.530 --> 00:31:46.330 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:31:46.330 --> 00:31:48.910 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: This is another piece
of this body of information

00:31:48.910 --> 00:31:54.340 align:middle line:84%
that really asks people to
suspend your disbelief in order

00:31:54.340 --> 00:31:57.720 align:middle line:90%
to think about this.

00:31:57.720 --> 00:32:01.690 align:middle line:84%
Most of us believe that it's
a one man, one soul world.

00:32:01.690 --> 00:32:02.490 align:middle line:90%
I have a soul.

00:32:02.490 --> 00:32:03.290 align:middle line:90%
You have a soul.

00:32:03.290 --> 00:32:04.120 align:middle line:90%
He has a good soul.

00:32:04.120 --> 00:32:05.220 align:middle line:90%
She's an old soul.

00:32:05.220 --> 00:32:07.920 align:middle line:84%
That's the vocabulary
that we use.

00:32:07.920 --> 00:32:10.870 align:middle line:84%
These angels said, gotta
change that vocabulary

00:32:10.870 --> 00:32:15.040 align:middle line:84%
because that's an
inaccurate way to say it.

00:32:15.040 --> 00:32:17.580 align:middle line:84%
The soul, the
level of human soul

00:32:17.580 --> 00:32:21.440 align:middle line:84%
is one unified field
of consciousness.

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:26.630 align:middle line:84%
It is this tree, this unified
field of consciousness

00:32:26.630 --> 00:32:30.600 align:middle line:90%
from which all of us emanate.

00:32:30.600 --> 00:32:31.910 align:middle line:90%
But it is unified.

00:32:31.910 --> 00:32:32.830 align:middle line:90%
It's not separate.

00:32:32.830 --> 00:32:36.750 align:middle line:84%
So what we're doing when we
say your soul and my soul

00:32:36.750 --> 00:32:40.420 align:middle line:84%
is that we're projecting
our sense of separation

00:32:40.420 --> 00:32:43.730 align:middle line:84%
into a realm of consciousness
that is not separate,

00:32:43.730 --> 00:32:46.880 align:middle line:84%
that is not separated,
that does not divide.

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:53.100 align:middle line:84%
So they just ask that we use
that word as a unifying word,

00:32:53.100 --> 00:32:56.060 align:middle line:84%
rather than as a separating
and identifying word.

00:32:56.060 --> 00:32:58.250 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Now, this gets
confusing for people.

00:32:58.250 --> 00:32:59.050 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Yes.

00:32:59.050 --> 00:33:01.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because you
get into a lot of other,

00:33:01.220 --> 00:33:04.500 align:middle line:84%
you know, ancient
religious traditions

00:33:04.500 --> 00:33:06.630 align:middle line:90%
and their definitions of soul.

00:33:06.630 --> 00:33:10.420 align:middle line:84%
And we talked about this in our
conversation on the telephone

00:33:10.420 --> 00:33:11.480 align:middle line:90%
a while back.

00:33:11.480 --> 00:33:14.950 align:middle line:84%
And that has--
this system is not

00:33:14.950 --> 00:33:18.150 align:middle line:84%
to say it's not recognizing
the individuated aspect

00:33:18.150 --> 00:33:21.980 align:middle line:84%
of that soul, that we are
each uniquely expressing.

00:33:21.980 --> 00:33:25.060 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: We are each
individuations of that soul.

00:33:25.060 --> 00:33:27.840 align:middle line:84%
And in form, we're
experiencing ourselves

00:33:27.840 --> 00:33:33.510 align:middle line:84%
as separate
individuations, in form.

00:33:33.510 --> 00:33:37.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And tell us why, tell
us the damage that they felt

00:33:37.960 --> 00:33:42.610 align:middle line:84%
was occurring on this
planet by people basically

00:33:42.610 --> 00:33:45.360 align:middle line:84%
locking into the
individuated part

00:33:45.360 --> 00:33:48.880 align:middle line:90%
and not focusing on the whole.

00:33:48.880 --> 00:33:53.080 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Well, the whole
is, the whole species

00:33:53.080 --> 00:33:55.890 align:middle line:90%
is the experiment, see.

00:33:55.890 --> 00:34:01.720 align:middle line:84%
There are birds, and there are
tigers, and there are dogs,

00:34:01.720 --> 00:34:04.360 align:middle line:84%
and there are lots of
different species, all of which

00:34:04.360 --> 00:34:06.350 align:middle line:90%
are doing their own thing.

00:34:06.350 --> 00:34:09.000 align:middle line:84%
But this experiment,
this human experiment,

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:13.710 align:middle line:84%
is one that we understand
as having free will.

00:34:13.710 --> 00:34:18.429 align:middle line:84%
So the experiment is, can
a species have free will

00:34:18.429 --> 00:34:23.500 align:middle line:84%
and stay in full alignment
with their highest intentions.

00:34:23.500 --> 00:34:25.000 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, how
we doing so far?

00:34:25.000 --> 00:34:27.120 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Yeah, not
doing so well so far.

00:34:27.120 --> 00:34:30.060 align:middle line:84%
That's why I think
they felt an urgency

00:34:30.060 --> 00:34:33.594 align:middle line:84%
about bringing this body
of information in now.

00:34:33.594 --> 00:34:35.260 align:middle line:84%
Now, what's interesting
is, as you said,

00:34:35.260 --> 00:34:37.080 align:middle line:84%
I published this
book 10 years ago.

00:34:37.080 --> 00:34:40.320 align:middle line:84%
So my sense of it was, OK, I'm
going to-- I'm going to-- well,

00:34:40.320 --> 00:34:42.940 align:middle line:84%
wait, I have to say,
I didn't publish

00:34:42.940 --> 00:34:44.721 align:middle line:90%
the book for a long time.

00:34:44.721 --> 00:34:46.679 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Didn't you--
you took another decade,

00:34:46.679 --> 00:34:48.553 align:middle line:84%
didn't you, just to play
with it with friends

00:34:48.553 --> 00:34:50.040 align:middle line:84%
and see if there
was truth in it.

00:34:50.040 --> 00:34:52.846 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: I did over
3,000 soul readings.

00:34:52.846 --> 00:34:53.929 align:middle line:90%
I call them soul readings.

00:34:53.929 --> 00:34:54.909 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: 3,000, wow,
that's due diligence.

00:34:54.909 --> 00:34:57.290 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Before I was--
before I was ready to say,

00:34:57.290 --> 00:34:59.290 align:middle line:84%
OK, this is real and
I'm going to publish it.

00:34:59.290 --> 00:35:00.998 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And the
people were responding?

00:35:00.998 --> 00:35:03.310 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Yes, people
were responding.

00:35:03.310 --> 00:35:04.640 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it was amazing.

00:35:04.640 --> 00:35:07.720 align:middle line:84%
Like, for example,
someone would come to me

00:35:07.720 --> 00:35:10.890 align:middle line:84%
and I would see
in their pattern,

00:35:10.890 --> 00:35:14.610 align:middle line:84%
that most of their principles
were ascending principles.

00:35:14.610 --> 00:35:18.570 align:middle line:84%
And so I would say to
them, you're barely human.

00:35:18.570 --> 00:35:20.320 align:middle line:90%
You're mostly a nature spirit.

00:35:20.320 --> 00:35:21.264 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:35:21.264 --> 00:35:23.430 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Which is kind of
a dangerous thing to say,

00:35:23.430 --> 00:35:26.020 align:middle line:90%
could be a hurtful thing to say.

00:35:26.020 --> 00:35:28.020 align:middle line:90%
But no, I would get tears.

00:35:28.020 --> 00:35:29.842 align:middle line:84%
Oh my god, I've
always known that.

00:35:29.842 --> 00:35:30.800 align:middle line:90%
I've always known that.

00:35:30.800 --> 00:35:33.490 align:middle line:84%
But I thought that was
what was wrong with me.

00:35:33.490 --> 00:35:37.130 align:middle line:84%
This is what is so interesting
about this body of information.

00:35:37.130 --> 00:35:41.670 align:middle line:84%
Often, what we find to be
true about our patterns

00:35:41.670 --> 00:35:44.600 align:middle line:84%
is what we thought
was broken about us.

00:35:44.600 --> 00:35:47.120 align:middle line:84%
And so when we read
that that is actually

00:35:47.120 --> 00:35:50.650 align:middle line:84%
what we came into this
incarnation to be,

00:35:50.650 --> 00:35:53.750 align:middle line:84%
we're liberated from
all that self-judgment.

00:35:53.750 --> 00:35:56.090 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's true,
because in your chart,

00:35:56.090 --> 00:35:58.630 align:middle line:84%
which I've seen in your
book, and in my chart,

00:35:58.630 --> 00:36:01.820 align:middle line:84%
we tend to live off of
the descending principles.

00:36:01.820 --> 00:36:06.040 align:middle line:84%
And how often do people say,
oh, yeah, that's-- she's-- pew--

00:36:06.040 --> 00:36:07.212 align:middle line:90%
she's out there.

00:36:07.212 --> 00:36:08.420 align:middle line:90%
You need to be more grounded.

00:36:08.420 --> 00:36:09.650 align:middle line:90%
That's pretty far out.

00:36:09.650 --> 00:36:11.150 align:middle line:90%
You know, she's out there.

00:36:11.150 --> 00:36:15.520 align:middle line:84%
And in reality, that's
exactly true but for purpose.

00:36:15.520 --> 00:36:16.320 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:36:16.320 --> 00:36:17.220 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Yeah, exactly.

00:36:17.220 --> 00:36:18.053 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: What's a--

00:36:18.053 --> 00:36:20.437 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: I found
my first reading

00:36:20.437 --> 00:36:22.770 align:middle line:84%
of my chart to just be one
of the most liberating things

00:36:22.770 --> 00:36:23.570 align:middle line:90%
ever.

00:36:23.570 --> 00:36:28.640 align:middle line:84%
You know, it's like, not
only am I mostly galactic,

00:36:28.640 --> 00:36:31.010 align:middle line:84%
but there's nothing
in my chart that

00:36:31.010 --> 00:36:34.130 align:middle line:84%
indicates that I should feel
guilty because I wasn't a,

00:36:34.130 --> 00:36:38.150 align:middle line:84%
you know, bra-burning
political activist in the '60s.

00:36:38.150 --> 00:36:38.950 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:36:38.950 --> 00:36:41.280 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: You know, and I
always felt guilty about that.

00:36:41.280 --> 00:36:42.821 align:middle line:84%
I always felt like
I should have been

00:36:42.821 --> 00:36:46.860 align:middle line:84%
out there marching and
doing and-- but I never did.

00:36:46.860 --> 00:36:47.680 align:middle line:90%
I never did it.

00:36:47.680 --> 00:36:48.610 align:middle line:90%
I just always--

00:36:48.610 --> 00:36:49.095 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: You had a more--

00:36:49.095 --> 00:36:49.810 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: And I
judged myself for it.

00:36:49.810 --> 00:36:52.750 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Kind of more of an
aloof cosmic view of things.

00:36:52.750 --> 00:36:53.630 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Yeah.

00:36:53.630 --> 00:36:55.679 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, and I felt
the same way, exactly.

00:36:55.679 --> 00:36:57.470 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't really one to
take to the streets.

00:36:57.470 --> 00:36:58.886 align:middle line:84%
But I was thinking
about all of it

00:36:58.886 --> 00:37:00.970 align:middle line:84%
and trying to put it
into a larger context

00:37:00.970 --> 00:37:01.770 align:middle line:90%
through the years.

00:37:01.770 --> 00:37:02.060 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Exactly.

00:37:02.060 --> 00:37:02.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: You know?

00:37:02.570 --> 00:37:03.510 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Exactly.

00:37:03.510 --> 00:37:06.576 align:middle line:84%
And so think about
this for a minute.

00:37:06.576 --> 00:37:11.140 align:middle line:84%
If you-- if you eliminate
all of those reasons

00:37:11.140 --> 00:37:15.810 align:middle line:84%
that you have to judge
yourself, and if you eliminate

00:37:15.810 --> 00:37:20.730 align:middle line:84%
all of those tendencies to
think up stuff to be afraid of,

00:37:20.730 --> 00:37:23.860 align:middle line:84%
think of the amount of
energy that gets released.

00:37:23.860 --> 00:37:24.660 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:37:24.660 --> 00:37:26.993 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: You've got all of
this energy that you've been

00:37:26.993 --> 00:37:30.710 align:middle line:84%
spending on self-judgment and
negative stuff, and then--

00:37:30.710 --> 00:37:32.190 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: You know, I love this.

00:37:32.190 --> 00:37:32.990 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:37:32.990 --> 00:37:35.350 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: And
then, you can-- you

00:37:35.350 --> 00:37:38.267 align:middle line:84%
can start living your life
in a very different way.

00:37:38.267 --> 00:37:40.850 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, so in truth-- in
