00:57:43.030 --> 00:57:46.330 align:middle line:84%
Chinese people,
most Asian people,

00:57:46.330 --> 00:57:51.320 align:middle line:84%
Indian people who operate
from different astrological

00:57:51.320 --> 00:57:52.350 align:middle line:90%
systems--

00:57:52.350 --> 00:57:53.010 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
the Vedic system.

00:57:53.010 --> 00:57:53.845 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Like the Vedic system.

00:57:53.845 --> 00:57:55.640 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That doesn't
plug into this the same.

00:57:55.640 --> 00:57:57.600 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Well, you know,
they just didn't tell me.

00:57:57.600 --> 00:57:59.830 align:middle line:84%
The angels haven't instructed
me about working with--

00:57:59.830 --> 00:58:01.010 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You didn't get
downloaded the Vedic version.

00:58:01.010 --> 00:58:01.900 align:middle line:90%
OK, gotcha.

00:58:01.900 --> 00:58:02.983 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: So I don't know.

00:58:02.983 --> 00:58:07.980 align:middle line:84%
But I would say, my willful
part of myself would say,

00:58:07.980 --> 00:58:10.470 align:middle line:84%
if you're born in India,
then I would probably

00:58:10.470 --> 00:58:13.367 align:middle line:84%
do a Vedic chart on you, rather
