00:58:13.367 --> 00:58:14.450 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, and see--

00:58:14.450 --> 00:58:15.960 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: It kind of
matters where you're born.

00:58:15.960 --> 00:58:16.680 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:58:16.680 --> 00:58:18.650 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: So I don't know
if I'm really qualified

00:58:18.650 --> 00:58:19.410 align:middle line:90%
to answer that question.

00:58:19.410 --> 00:58:20.100 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's OK.

00:58:20.100 --> 00:58:22.050 align:middle line:84%
That was just something
that occurred to me to ask.

00:58:22.050 --> 00:58:22.850 align:middle line:90%
>>KAPLAN: Yeah.

00:58:22.850 --> 00:58:25.890 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: What is your primary
principle that shows itself,

