00:58:33.580 --> 00:58:34.380 align:middle line:90%
challenging.

00:58:34.380 --> 00:58:35.990 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let's
talk about humility.

00:58:35.990 --> 00:58:36.790 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:58:36.790 --> 00:58:37.230 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about it.

00:58:37.230 --> 00:58:38.825 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: You noticed I
skipped right over humility.

00:58:38.825 --> 00:58:39.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, you did.

00:58:39.570 --> 00:58:41.440 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: Humility is one of
the descending principles.

00:58:41.440 --> 00:58:42.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:58:42.240 --> 00:58:44.980 align:middle line:84%
>>KAPLAN: And the
definition of humility, it

00:58:44.980 --> 00:58:47.410 align:middle line:84%
